headline: Avery Dennison (AVY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: What a brutal six months it’s been for Avery Dennison. The stock has dropped 24.1% and now trades at $165.51, rattling many shareholders. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
